      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of June 6 article: Russell J Verney did not say Ross Perot invited Patrick J Buchanan to seek Reform Party presidential nomination</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An article on Tuesday about Ross Perot's inclination against running for the Reform Party nomination for president referred inaccurately to party officials' approach to Patrick J. Buchanan. Senior party officials have said that associates of Mr. Perot let Mr. Buchanan know he was welcome to seek the nomination. Russell J. Verney, an associate of Mr. Perot, did not say that Mr. Perot invited Mr. Buchanan to run.</p>
      </block>
